channel.title: Need help with a 728 server project from scratch
channel.description:
Hello all,
I'm kinda new to the rsps coding scene, altough I already have alot of Java experience. I'm planning on programming a 728 server from scratch. After looking in some of the popular sources, there are a few things that I don't really understand yet of the RS network protocol (encoding, decoding etc). I hope there is someone here that can help me with some problems I'm facing about setting up the very, very base of a 728 server via Skype.
Add me, Masterleik, or send me a PM. It would be greatly appreciated.
Thanks!
Basaa
